import { Box, Flex, Grid, GridItem, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

export default function Footer() {
  return (
    <Flex lineHeight="1" fontSize="14px" p="0px 50px"
          ml="80px" color= '#666' bg='#fff'   
          fontFamily="OpenSans,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"
    > 
         {/*
    width="100%" display="flex"     display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: baseline;
*/}
        <Box textAlign="center">
            <Text>Popular Searchs:</Text>
        </Box>
        <Grid columnGap="1px" m="0px 0px 0px 30px" alignItems="start" templateRows='repeat(2, 1fr)' templateColumns='repeat(7, 1fr)' >
            <GridItem>realme buds q</GridItem>
            <GridItem>xiaomi redmi 7 case</GridItem>
            <Text>lenevo Ip1s tws</Text>
            <Text>5g phone</Text>
            <Text>projector 4k</Text>
            <Text>mens's sports shoes</Text>
            <Text>creality ender 3</Text>
            <Text>xiaomi mi band 5</Text>
            <Text>led light strip</Text>
            <Text>360s7 robot vaccum cleaner</Text>
            <Text>amazfit gts 2</Text>
            <Text>roborock s5 max</Text>
            <Text>xiaomi vaccum</Text>
            <Text>poco x3 nfc</Text>
        </Grid>
    </Flex>
  )
}
